TIL that alien abduction stories are probably based on sleep paralysis, a condition where you wake up, dream-hallucinate someone in your room, and can't move..
John Keel actually posited something like this in his book "The Mothman Prophecies". Although John Still thinks the states were induced by a non-human entity.
